      "content": "• Positive: There's a sofa. / There are two armchairs.\n• Question: Is there a TV? / Are there any pictures?\n• Negative: There isn't a computer. / There aren't any photographs.\n• Prepositions: in, on, under, next to"
    },
    "ja": {
      "title": "文法のポイント",
      "content": "• 肯定文: There's a sofa.（ソファがあります。） / There are two armchairs.（アームチェアが二つあります。）\n• 疑問文: Is there a TV?（テレビはありますか？） / Are there any pictures?（絵はありますか？）\n• 否定文: There isn't a computer.（コンピューターはありません。） / There aren't any photographs.（写真はありません。）\n• 前置詞: in（～の中に）, on（～の上に）, under（～の下に）, next to（～の隣に）"
    },
    "fr": {
      "title": "Point de Grammaire",
      "content": "• Positif: There's a sofa. / There are two armchairs.\n• Question: Is there a TV? / Are there any pictures?\n• Négatif: There isn't a computer. / There aren't any photographs.\n• Prépositions: in, on, under, next to"
    },
